imdb.plot outline: Introducing Smart Cookies Dallas, a new interview series supported by the City of Dallas Office of Cultural Affairs featuring some of our city's most dynamic female talent. From established local icons like Vicki Meek and Marianne Gargour to multi-talent wonders like Stormi Demerson, Anastasia Munoz and Holly"LEV" Peyton to up-and-comers like Karissa F Leicht, host Jenni Tooley explores how artists balance their personal, business and professional lives while creating an impact. We'll also showcase Dallas locations like the Deep Ellum Art Company, South Dallas Cultural Center, Continental Gin Building, Arts Mission Oak Cliff, Grand Park and Wilson Building.
imdb.title: Smart Cookies with Jenni Tooley
